<function>

access:   public

name: join

param: string|object, $spec

param: string, $cond

param: array|string, $cols, NULL

return: Solar_Sql_Select

</function>

Adds a JOIN table and columns to the query.

* Parameters:

 * string|object //$spec//: If a Solar_Sql_Table object, the table to join to; if a string, the table name to join to.

 * string //$cond//: Join on this condition.

 * array|string //$cols//: The columns to select from the joined table.

* Returns Solar_Sql_Select

Adds a JOIN table and columns to the query.